    "title": "Adam na Hawa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "adam na hawa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Adamu alikuwa mwanadamu wa kwanza na baba wa ubinadamu. Mungu aliumba wanandoa wa kwanza kwa sura yake ili wajaze dunia na kusimamia uumbaji (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:31\">Mwanzo 1:26–31</a>). Mungu alimuumba Adamu kutoka kwa udongo na kumpa uhai (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">Mwanzo 2:7</a>). Majukumu ya Adamu yalijumuisha:</p><ul><li><p>Kutunza bustani ambayo Mungu alimuweka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">Mwanzo 2:15</a>)</p></li><li><p>Kuwapatia wanyama majina (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:19-Gen2:20\">Mwanzo 2:19–20</a>)</p></li><li><p>Kutii maagizo ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">Mwanzo 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">2:16–17</a>)</p></li></ul><p>Mungu alimuumba mwanamke wa kwanza kuwa mwenzi na msaidizi wa Adamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:18-Gen2:22\">Mwanzo 2:18–22</a>). Uumbaji wa Hawa kutoka kwenye ubavu wa Adamu unaonyesha umoja ambao Mungu alikusudia kwa ajili ya ndoa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:23-Gen2:25\">Mwanzo 2:23–25</a>). Anaheshimiwa kama &quot;mama wa wote walio hai&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:20\">Mwanzo 3:20</a>).</p><p>Baada ya nyoka kumdanganya Hawa kukataa utawala wa Mungu, Adamu pia alikosa utii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:6\">Mwanzo 3:1–6</a>). Kutotii kwao kwa makusudi kuliharibu uhusiano wao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:7\">Mwanzo 3:7</a>). Kutotii kwao pia kuliwatenganisha na Mungu. Mungu alimtafuta Adamu baada ya uasi wake. Yeye na Hawa walikuwa wakijificha kati ya miti, tayari wakihisi kutengwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8\">Mwanzo 3:8</a>).</p><p>Wakati Mungu alipomuuliza, Adamu alimlaumu Hawa na kwa njia isiyo ya moja kwa moja alimlaumu Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:12\">Mwanzo 3:12</a>). Uasi wao ulisababisha maumivu, mahusiano yaliyovurugika, ugumu katika kutawala dunia, na kifo cha kimwili na kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:19\">Mwanzo 3:16–19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22-Gen3:24\">22–24</a>). Hata hivyo, Mungu alitoa ngozi za wanyama ili kuwafunika Adamu na Hawa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:21\">Mwanzo 3:21</a>). Mungu aliahidi kwamba uzao wa Hawa utamshinda Shetani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">Mwanzo 3:15</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:20\">Warumi 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:1-Rev12:9\">Ufunuo 12:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:1-Rev20:10\">20:1–10</a>).</p><p>Adam alikuwa mtu wa kihistoria (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:25\">Mwanzo 4:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1-Gen5:5\">5:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr1:1\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:7\">Hosea 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:38\">Luka 3:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:14\">Warumi 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1 Wakorintho 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:45\">45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:13-1Tim2:14\">1 Timotheo 2:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:14\">Yuda 1:14</a>). Adam pia anawakilisha ubinadamu wote. Amri za Mungu katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:30\">Mwanzo 1:26–30</a> na laana katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:19\">3:16–19</a> ziliathiri siyo tu Adam na Hawa bali kila mtu. Adam anawakilisha kutengana na Mungu ambako watu wote hupitia.</p><p>Mtume Paulo alilinganisha watu wanaowakilishwa na Adamu, Adamu wa kwanza, na wale wanaomfuata Yesu Kristo, &quot;Adamu wa mwisho&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:21\">Warumi 5:12–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:45-1Cor15:50\">1 Wakorintho 15:45–50</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:11\">Warumi 8:5–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20-Rom8:22\">20–22</a>). Watu wanaowakilishwa na Adamu wanaishi kama yeye. Wanashiriki katika dhambi yake, kutengwa na Mungu na uumbaji, na kifo cha kiroho. Kinyume chake, wale wanaomfuata Yesu wanaishi kwa imani ndani yake. Wanabadilishwa kuwa mfano wa Kristo na kuwa &quot;watu wapya&quot; wanaoshiriki katika uumbaji mpya (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">Warumi 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1 Wakorintho 15:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2 Wakorintho 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:15\">Wagalatia 6:15</a>). Yesu huondoa vizuizi vilivyowekwa na Adamu na Hawa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">Warumi 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:19\">2 Wakorintho 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:27-Gal3:28\">Wagalatia 3:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:14-Eph2:16\">Waefeso 2:14–16</a>). Yesu anarejesha kile walichopoteza.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:31\">Mwanzo 1:26–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:4-Gen3:24\">2:4–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:25-Gen5:5\">4:25–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6-Hos6:7\">Hosea 6:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:38\">Luka 3:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:21\">Warumi 5:12–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1 Wakorintho 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:45-1Cor15:49\">45–49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:13-1Tim2:14\">1 Timotheo 2:13–14</a></p>",
